def is_imid_drug(drug_name):
    imid_drugs = {"thalidomide", "lenalidomide", "pomalidomide", 
                  "mezigdomide", "iberdomide", "golcadomide"}
    return drug_name.lower() in imid_drugs

This function checks if the input drug name (case-insensitive) matches any known IMiD drug names and returns a boolean result.
